{"tid":1242268,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(158-Day) 反攻區議會行動","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T06:20:54.000Z","uid":263331,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b758a7b7c9d3be1a215109f3e48bd872cad1dccf","tid":1242268,"uid":263331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:50:03.000Z","msg":"香港合共458名區議員，每區三、四十個席位~<br />\n<br />\n因為選區分到好細，往往當選只係贏幾百票，只要團結，有系統𠝹建制票、做好Online/ Offline文宣，應該有希望重奪地區議會～<br />\n<br />\n1. 每大區（甚至每分區）成位fb/tg 策略群組<br />\n2. \b檢視以往數屆選區選民Composition，集中火力攻最有勝選分區<br />\n3. 盡早協調參選人（小心DQ，可先參選，後棄選）<br />\n4. 派出真建制小隊𠝹票 （要注意法律問題，舞弊及非法行為）<br />\n5. 為每區建制議員著書立說，撰寫過往「豐功偉績」，人物利益關係圖等等<br />\n6. 組織選民登記小隊 <br />\n7. 組織街站工作小隊 ( 靚仔靚女/ Model）<br />\n8. 組織文宣工作小隊（designer / researcher / photographer) /區會以往集中民生議案<br />\n9. 組織公關小隊（PR/ digital marketer/ Youtuber/ KOL etc) <br />\n<br />\n投票日定為今年11月24日, <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只剩158日</span></span><br />\n<br />\n選舉資料<br />\n舞弊及非法行為<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/pdf/distco/2015dc/guideline/ch/dc_ch16.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fpdf%2Fdistco%2F2015dc%2Fguideline%2Fch%2Fdc_ch16.pdf&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dTBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=462e45e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/pdf/distco/2015dc/guideline/ch/dc_ch16.pdf</a><br />\n選舉指引<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/dc_guide.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fch%2Fdistco%2Fdc_guide.htm&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dTBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=2c3e3c1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/dc_guide.htm</a><br />\n2015選票結果<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2015/chi/results.html?1560915885059\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fdc2015%2Fchi%2Fresults.html%3F1560915885059&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dTBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=14a5c7c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2015/chi/results.html?1560915885059</a><br />\n2019分區<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/2019dc_elect_map.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fch%2Fdistco%2F2019dc_elect_map.htm&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dTBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=707c6b53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/2019dc_elect_map.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d6f67a64f7be35fa50af2a9fe5a48ed29c8078f8","tid":1242268,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fe04f60ecf4e7d93d1cf7d92349a7c539e1802","tid":1242268,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:51:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2bf0eb7b0df931aa40a436dc9bbd83625541d21b","tid":1242268,"uid":263331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"afda7cfb621c133c676d881cba0f3b3374611491","tid":1242268,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:03:08.000Z","msg":"仲有一樣係教統局追究老師責任<br />\n我哋要先係呢幾日嘅事件上站穩陣腳<br />\n再同市民講政府不可信<br />\n要改組政府<br />\n重新訂立可行有效嘅監察機制<br />\n之後嘅事之後再講"},{"pid":"8024c0d07cffbf632c8456e1a9beb2c54d3b0597","tid":1242268,"uid":84633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:20:54.000Z","msg":"潛在參選人士<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89#%E8%AD%B0%E5%B8%AD%E6%95%B8%E7%9B%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2019%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%23%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%259B%25AE&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dTBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=95cc0456\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89#%E8%AD%B0%E5%B8%AD%E6%95%B8%E7%9B%AE</a>"}]}